      <title>朝中社称，朝鲜金正恩将与中国发展长期关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-develop-long-standing-ties-with-china-kcna-says-2024-04-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜官方媒体朝中社周日援引金正恩与中国最高立法委员赵乐际会面的消息称，朝鲜领导人金正恩重申了与中国发展长期关系的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-develop-long-standing-ties-with-china-kcna-says-2024-04-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 21:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
